WEBVTT

00:31.907 --> 00:34.201
VINCENT: <i>Congratulations</i>
<i>on your big win, Kai.</i>

00:34.284 --> 00:36.662
I couldn't be more proud.

00:37.663 --> 00:39.748
I have to stay sharp.

00:40.374 --> 00:42.292
For the men.

00:44.461 --> 00:45.838
How's your leg?

00:45.921 --> 00:47.923
It's, uh, it's stiff.

00:48.006 --> 00:50.175
But it's good.

00:50.300 --> 00:52.219
I'll live.

00:55.556 --> 00:58.684
I got your edible arrangement
in the hospital, by the way.

00:59.518 --> 01:00.936
It was very thoughtful.

01:01.395 --> 01:03.021
I figured the reason you didn't
come visit me yourself

01:03.105 --> 01:05.023
was because you were ashamed.

01:05.107 --> 01:08.527
I mean, it was your patient
who colluded with the woman

01:08.610 --> 01:09.820
who tried to murder me.

01:10.320 --> 01:11.738
(sighs)

01:11.822 --> 01:13.949
Allyson Mayfair-Richards
is a sick woman.

01:18.078 --> 01:20.706
But you're not far off,
I was ashamed.

01:21.456 --> 01:23.292
I mean, you've accomplished
so much, Kai.

01:23.375 --> 01:26.879
Running for office,
starting a whole movement.

01:27.421 --> 01:29.923
And I didn't know
about any of it.

01:30.924 --> 01:32.843
I'm just proud of you.

01:35.095 --> 01:37.181
I don't need you
to play Dad, Vincent.

01:37.264 --> 01:39.266
You're just as bad at it
as he was.

01:39.349 --> 01:40.517
I look after myself.

01:40.601 --> 01:41.727
You think that I want to be

01:41.810 --> 01:43.270
like that prick, Kai?

01:43.353 --> 01:44.646
No.

01:44.730 --> 01:47.858
I'm-I'm trying to apologize.

01:48.150 --> 01:50.235
Listen, what you are
doing here--

01:50.319 --> 01:52.988
organizing all of these people,

01:53.071 --> 01:55.449
making a difference--
it's awesome.

01:59.536 --> 02:00.871
You think so?

02:00.954 --> 02:02.789
Absolutely.

02:02.873 --> 02:05.167
And I want to help you
get your message out.

02:05.250 --> 02:07.211
With the right strategy,

02:07.294 --> 02:09.505
this could be
a national movement.

02:11.173 --> 02:13.133
-Yes.
-Yes.

02:14.134 --> 02:15.886
You know, I was thinking
about making some videos

02:15.969 --> 02:17.054
for social media.

02:17.137 --> 02:18.430
-(snaps fingers)
-That's genius.

02:18.514 --> 02:19.973
And I-I could film it.

02:27.981 --> 02:29.149
Thanks, big bro.

02:29.650 --> 02:31.193
Of course.

02:31.276 --> 02:33.946
Oh, there's just one more thing
I need from you.

02:34.279 --> 02:36.823
From now on,
call me Councilman.

03:57.571 --> 03:59.948
(low chatter)

04:09.708 --> 04:12.920
-Enjoy your meal.
-(spits)

04:13.003 --> 04:15.172
I'm not eating this shit.

04:15.255 --> 04:18.300
Kai told us to start making you
healthy food.

04:18.383 --> 04:21.428
(laughs) You bitches
are so sensitive.

04:21.637 --> 04:24.223
You know, your bangability

04:24.306 --> 04:27.100
would go way up
if you just smiled.

04:29.269 --> 04:30.896
Ooh.

04:30.979 --> 04:32.731
(laughter)

04:34.983 --> 04:36.443
(knife clatters)

04:38.779 --> 04:41.031
GUTTERBALL: She does have
a nice ass, though.

04:45.410 --> 04:48.247
I can't put up with this <i>shit</i>
much longer!

04:48.330 --> 04:50.582
I'm being treated like a servant
in my own restaurant.

04:50.666 --> 04:53.085
How did this Handmaid shit
even happen?

04:53.168 --> 04:54.878
48 hours ago,
we were on the verge

04:54.962 --> 04:56.296
of toppling the patriarchy!

04:56.380 --> 04:58.632
That's before he had
a goddamn army.

04:58.715 --> 04:59.883
That's not an army!

05:00.008 --> 05:01.051
That's a bunch of dude-bros

05:01.134 --> 05:02.344
with too much time
on their hands.

05:02.427 --> 05:04.221
Yeah? Tell that to
the other city council members.

05:04.304 --> 05:05.556
You weren't at that meeting
last night.

05:15.732 --> 05:17.484
That's six votes in favor.

05:19.236 --> 05:21.280
Perry?

05:25.367 --> 05:29.454
I understand the appeal
of private security,

05:29.538 --> 05:31.957
but we already have
a police force,

05:32.040 --> 05:34.585
not to mention countless community

05:34.668 --> 05:36.879
neighborhood watch groups.

05:36.962 --> 05:38.547
Do we really want to spend
taxpayer money

05:38.630 --> 05:40.632
to put more men with guns

05:40.716 --> 05:43.177
on the streets
in our neighborhoods?

05:43.552 --> 05:45.721
That makes me uncomfortable.

05:48.265 --> 05:49.850
Really?

05:50.684 --> 05:52.436
I know you live
in a gated community.

05:53.896 --> 05:55.772
Not everyone can afford that.

05:56.899 --> 05:58.650
And even your two beautiful
daughters have to leave

05:58.734 --> 06:00.986
those gates to go to school,
don't they?

06:01.236 --> 06:03.530
12 and 16, am I right?

06:03.655 --> 06:05.115
Now, just how comfortable

06:05.199 --> 06:08.994
would you feel
if something terrible

06:09.077 --> 06:10.746
were to happen to them?

06:10.829 --> 06:12.915
You'd never forgive yourself,
would you?

06:14.166 --> 06:16.084
I vote yes.

06:16.168 --> 06:19.046
KAI: And with that,
the motion passes.

06:19.129 --> 06:20.714
(gavel bangs)

06:20.797 --> 06:23.550
BEVERLY: <i>We let this shit go</i>
<i>too far already.</i>

06:23.634 --> 06:25.052
But I've been thinking
about this.

06:25.135 --> 06:26.887
Those boys are just grunts.

06:26.970 --> 06:30.057
They don't so much as take
a shit unless he tells them to.

06:30.140 --> 06:31.558
But if we cut off the head
of the snake,

06:32.434 --> 06:34.561
the entire army falls.

06:34.770 --> 06:37.898
You can't go after Kai.
It'd be a suicide mission.

06:37.981 --> 06:39.650
And I don't just mean us,
I mean the movement.

06:39.733 --> 06:40.901
We need him.

06:40.984 --> 06:42.444
Why do you keep on
defending him?

06:42.528 --> 06:45.656
Look, I'm not happy about being
put on kitchen duty, either,

06:45.739 --> 06:48.325
but it's all part
of his larger plan.

06:48.408 --> 06:50.035
There is no plan.

06:50.118 --> 06:52.829
He is not fit to lead.

06:52.913 --> 06:54.456
-You don't know him.
-You have to decide

06:54.540 --> 06:57.459
if you are with us
or against us.

06:57.543 --> 06:59.920
You think big brother's
gonna spare you?

07:00.003 --> 07:01.964
Reward your loyalty?

07:02.214 --> 07:03.632
Wake up, little girl.

07:03.715 --> 07:05.008
Kai's gonna do whatever
he needs to do

07:05.092 --> 07:06.510
to get what he wants,

07:06.593 --> 07:09.263
even if that includes
sacrificing baby sis.

07:09.346 --> 07:11.348
He does not give a shit
about you.

07:11.431 --> 07:12.975
You're wrong!

07:13.225 --> 07:14.601
Kai would never hurt me.

07:14.810 --> 07:16.645
I wouldn't even be here
if it weren't for him.

07:19.022 --> 07:20.983
WINTER: <i>It was two years ago.</i>
<i>Halloween.</i>

07:21.275 --> 07:22.860
<i>We were doing</i>
<i>what we always did:</i>

07:22.943 --> 07:26.029
<i>trolling the social justice</i>
<i>warriors.</i>

07:26.113 --> 07:27.114
<i>But that was too easy.</i>

07:27.447 --> 07:30.951
"Why should we allow abortion

07:31.034 --> 07:34.037
"for the health of the mother

07:34.121 --> 07:38.166
"when the baby is the only part
of that duo

07:38.250 --> 07:39.793
without sin?"

07:39.877 --> 07:42.296
(laughing)

07:42.379 --> 07:44.882
KAI: "Kill the mother,
save the baby."

07:44.965 --> 07:48.177
WINTER: <i>We hit the jackpot</i>
<i>in the Dark Web.</i>

07:48.260 --> 07:50.762
<i>We would pretend to be one</i>
<i>of the true believers,</i>

07:50.846 --> 07:53.182
<i>then we would go farther than</i>
<i>anyone could possibly go.</i>

07:53.265 --> 07:56.476
Wait, I got one.
Okay...

07:56.560 --> 08:00.564
"Man can never escape
from temptation

08:00.647 --> 08:03.692
"because, in birth,
he passes through the vagina,

08:03.775 --> 08:06.737
"which has been desecrated
by the filthy act

08:06.820 --> 08:08.363
of sexual intercourse."
(smacks lips)

08:08.447 --> 08:09.865
-(laughs) Get out.
-(message alert chimes)

08:09.948 --> 08:11.074
<i>That was when we got</i>
<i>a private message from someone</i>

08:11.158 --> 08:12.326
<i>named Pastor Charles.</i>

08:12.409 --> 08:14.036
"You are worthy
of an invitation"?

08:14.119 --> 08:15.370
-Wait, from who?
-Yes!

08:15.454 --> 08:16.538
These people are dangerous, Kai.

08:16.622 --> 08:17.623
KAI:
They're posers.

08:17.706 --> 08:18.832
Messing with them in person

08:18.916 --> 08:20.542
will be a million times
more fun.

08:20.626 --> 08:24.505
KAI: Whoa! Judgment House?

08:24.588 --> 08:26.089
We're going.

08:27.216 --> 08:29.468
WINTER: <i>Judgment House turned</i>
<i>out to be a farm in Wixom</i>

08:29.551 --> 08:31.845
<i>near Highway 96.</i>

08:32.804 --> 08:35.182
Time to see the animals
in their cages.

08:35.265 --> 08:37.059
Where's everyone else?

08:37.142 --> 08:39.144
(door creaks)

08:40.729 --> 08:41.939
Hello, brother.

08:42.022 --> 08:44.441
Pastor Charles, I presume.

08:44.525 --> 08:46.527
I brought my sister, Winter.

08:46.610 --> 08:47.945
What is this place?

08:48.028 --> 08:50.864
Oh, it's a house of mirth to some.

08:51.281 --> 08:54.910
The portent to those whose eyes
are open but cannot see.

08:57.955 --> 09:01.250
Once you enter, you agree
to never share the provenance

09:01.333 --> 09:03.961
of what you've seen inside.

09:05.420 --> 09:08.215
Our secret to have and to hold.

09:08.298 --> 09:10.008
Till death do us part?

09:11.802 --> 09:14.638
Punishment is your
everlasting soul.

09:14.721 --> 09:17.140
(door creaks shut)

09:19.142 --> 09:21.061
I'm the watchman.

09:22.062 --> 09:23.480
This way.

09:37.744 --> 09:39.830
(door closes)

09:46.253 --> 09:47.921
(door slams shut)

09:48.463 --> 09:50.507
Shit. The door's locked.

09:50.591 --> 09:52.009
Well...

09:53.886 --> 09:55.095
...only one way to go.

10:01.059 --> 10:02.144
(flames whooshing)

10:02.227 --> 10:03.645
(recording of baby crying)

10:03.729 --> 10:06.607
PASTOR CHARLES (over speaker):
<i>Who shall speak for the unborn?</i>

10:06.690 --> 10:07.900
(recording of baby crying continues)

10:07.983 --> 10:10.736
WOMAN (moaning):
Help me. Help me.

10:12.446 --> 10:14.448
I killed my baby.

10:16.241 --> 10:18.285
Now I'm bleeding to death.

10:18.368 --> 10:19.661
(whimpers)

10:19.745 --> 10:21.079
Bummer.

10:22.247 --> 10:24.374
(quietly)
Help me, please.

10:24.458 --> 10:27.586
He kidnapped me.
He's making me do this.

10:28.921 --> 10:30.047
This isn't a show.

10:30.130 --> 10:31.965
(cries)
This is not a show.

10:32.049 --> 10:34.760
-What the fuck?
-She's really good.

10:34.843 --> 10:36.011
-(whimpering) No, no.
-You're good.

10:36.094 --> 10:37.888
-(sobbing)
-This... Jesus Christ.

10:37.971 --> 10:39.598
(sniffs)

10:39.681 --> 10:41.266
(sobbing)

10:41.350 --> 10:42.434
This is real blood.

10:42.518 --> 10:44.186
(sobbing)
Help me.

10:44.269 --> 10:46.313
Help me.

10:47.356 --> 10:48.774
PASTOR CHARLES:
<i>Wide is the gate</i>

10:48.857 --> 10:51.193
and broad the way

10:51.276 --> 10:53.570
which leadeth to destruction.

10:54.112 --> 10:55.531
(buzzing)

10:58.825 --> 11:00.327
WINTER: <i>We got to get</i>
<i>out of here. Come on.</i>

11:00.410 --> 11:02.788
KAI: <i>Whoa, whoa, wait, wait,</i>
<i>wait. Wait, wait, wait. Wait.</i>

11:02.871 --> 11:04.122
(woman whimpering)

11:04.206 --> 11:05.249
-Shit!
-(panting)

11:05.332 --> 11:07.084
WINTER:
<i>I knew after the first room,</i>

11:07.167 --> 11:08.794
<i>that what we saw was real.</i>

11:11.630 --> 11:13.549
<i>Not actors in a haunted house.</i>

11:13.799 --> 11:16.009
It smells like death in here.

11:25.227 --> 11:27.563
PASTOR CHARLES: Behold
the whirlwind of the Lord.

11:27.646 --> 11:31.108
It shall fall with pain
upon the head of the wicked.

11:32.025 --> 11:33.402
KAI:
He's alive.

11:39.575 --> 11:40.951
Hey, man.

11:44.371 --> 11:45.664
-(screaming)
-Aah!

11:46.164 --> 11:47.666
No more.

11:48.250 --> 11:51.837
He's corrupted me
by the drugs of my choice:

11:51.920 --> 11:55.841
ecstasy, cocaine, opioids.

11:55.924 --> 11:58.510
My body is a bag of mush.

11:58.677 --> 12:01.513
I'm dying from the inside out.

12:01.597 --> 12:02.723
WINTER:
Oh, my God.

12:02.806 --> 12:04.725
Get the fuck out of here.

12:05.976 --> 12:07.603
What of the sodomite?

12:07.686 --> 12:09.062
(loud bang, door creaks open)

12:12.316 --> 12:14.735
MAN: (sobbing quietly)
Help me, please.

12:20.032 --> 12:21.533
Please...

12:21.617 --> 12:23.952
you got to get me out of here.

12:24.328 --> 12:26.330
The seducer of the innocent...

12:26.663 --> 12:30.334
toward the wicked filth
of strange flesh.

12:30.792 --> 12:33.170
-Did the Lord not say...
<i>-Come on, Kai, we have to go.</i>

12:33.253 --> 12:34.254
No!

12:34.338 --> 12:36.298
<i>...that man shall not</i>
<i>lie with man as with woman?</i>

12:36.590 --> 12:39.760
-He can't do this to people.
-It is an abomination!

12:39.843 --> 12:42.137
<i>The blood shall be</i>
<i>on their heads.</i>

12:42.679 --> 12:46.225
<i>The Lord destroyed</i>
Sodom and Gomorrah

12:46.308 --> 12:48.143
<i>with fire and brimstone.</i>

12:48.227 --> 12:50.479
Behold, His judgment is...

12:50.938 --> 12:53.982
<i>it is ever swift and divine!</i>

12:54.316 --> 12:55.943
<i>And in uncertain times,</i>

12:56.026 --> 12:58.070
<i>-what vengeance</i>
-When he finishes talking...

12:58.153 --> 12:59.363
<i>shall mark their days?</i>

12:59.446 --> 13:01.323
...knives will burst
through my chest.

13:01.406 --> 13:03.450
PASTOR CHARLES:
<i>A plague to slow their way...</i>

13:03.534 --> 13:05.369
MAN: I saw it happen
to the guy before me.

13:05.452 --> 13:07.788
...or the strike
of swift justice!

13:08.205 --> 13:09.790
-Holy shit.
-I don't want to see this anymore.

13:09.873 --> 13:11.500
No, we have
to get him out of here.

13:11.583 --> 13:13.669
PASTOR CHARLES: <i>His judgment</i>
is ever swift!

13:13.752 --> 13:14.878
Help me!

13:14.962 --> 13:16.505
PASTOR CHARLES (softly):
<i>His punishment</i>

13:16.588 --> 13:19.883
<i>a slow... burning...</i>

13:19.967 --> 13:21.510
fire.

13:21.593 --> 13:22.803
(trembling breath)

13:24.137 --> 13:26.223
MAN: (whimpering)
<i>Oh, my God. Hurry.</i>

13:27.182 --> 13:29.059
(man trembling, panting)

13:29.142 --> 13:31.311
Go get help. We're getting
everyone out of here.

13:31.395 --> 13:33.105
Now!

13:36.733 --> 13:37.985
Come on.

13:43.365 --> 13:44.867
(quietly) Shit.

13:46.243 --> 13:47.911
WINTER: No...

14:00.757 --> 14:01.967
Shit.

14:07.639 --> 14:10.475
Yes. I see in your eyes

14:10.559 --> 14:12.144
a true connection

14:12.227 --> 14:14.479
to the wretched souls in here.

14:17.524 --> 14:20.527
I think you need to be
in the show.

14:22.112 --> 14:24.531
-(thump)
-(grunts)

14:24.615 --> 14:25.908
(gasps softly)

14:28.035 --> 14:30.078
KAI:
<i>Okay, you sick bastard,</i>

14:30.162 --> 14:32.122
this girl you kidnapped
after her appointment

14:32.206 --> 14:33.332
at Planned Parenthood,

14:33.415 --> 14:35.209
and all she had was a UTI.

14:36.251 --> 14:38.128
This guy, you took from rehab

14:38.212 --> 14:40.130
when he was trying to sober up.

14:40.214 --> 14:42.466
And my friend here
was at an AIDS clinic

14:42.549 --> 14:44.301
volunteering his time.

14:45.886 --> 14:47.429
How many people
have you condemned

14:47.513 --> 14:49.348
for no reason?

14:51.308 --> 14:53.519
I do not answer

14:53.602 --> 14:55.729
to you or your laws.

14:56.104 --> 14:57.523
GIRL:
We're gonna call

14:57.606 --> 15:00.067
the police, and then
you're going to prison.

15:01.026 --> 15:02.569
KAI:
That's not justice.

15:02.653 --> 15:05.113
He doesn't deserve anything less

15:05.531 --> 15:08.116
than what he was willing
to put you through.

15:17.334 --> 15:19.711
I say we do what's right.

15:21.922 --> 15:23.215
Winter?

15:23.298 --> 15:25.092
(Pastor Charles mumbles inaudibly)

15:27.719 --> 15:29.513
Kill the motherfucker.

15:42.776 --> 15:45.195
WINTER: <i>Everything changed</i>
<i>after Pastor Charles.</i>

15:45.279 --> 15:48.448
<i>He started popping Adderall,</i>
<i>went deeper into the Dark Web,</i>

15:48.532 --> 15:50.659
<i>but he realized</i>
<i>he can't save everyone.</i>

15:50.742 --> 15:53.787
<i>Better to burn it all down</i>
<i>and build a new world.</i>

15:53.871 --> 15:56.248
<i>I know you guys hate him</i>
<i>right now,</i>

15:56.331 --> 15:57.791
he's lost his way,

15:57.875 --> 16:00.669
but we can put him back
on the right path.

16:00.752 --> 16:02.880
I'll go to him.

16:02.963 --> 16:04.965
He'll listen to me.

16:06.049 --> 16:07.676
(softly) I know, baby.

16:07.759 --> 16:09.178
You're right.

16:10.387 --> 16:11.889
BEVERLY:
Fine.

16:11.972 --> 16:13.891
We'll try it your way.

16:14.474 --> 16:16.143
But come the end of the week,

16:16.226 --> 16:18.187
if I'm still
in this goddamn kitchen,

16:18.270 --> 16:20.397
I'm coming for your brother.

16:21.231 --> 16:23.567
And you better get
the hell out of my way.

16:35.078 --> 16:36.747
KAI: So...

16:36.830 --> 16:38.373
the girls are restless.

16:38.457 --> 16:40.209
WINTER: No. We just feel
kind of left out.

16:40.292 --> 16:43.837
I mean, Jesus, Kai, you have us
working in a kitchen.

16:43.921 --> 16:46.381
Well, I was gonna put Harrison
in the kitchen, but...

16:46.465 --> 16:47.966
somebody killed him.

16:48.050 --> 16:50.177
You're still mad about that?

16:50.260 --> 16:53.263
No. Actually, I'm not.

16:58.185 --> 16:59.645
Come here.

17:00.103 --> 17:01.522
Sit with me.

17:21.375 --> 17:23.794
(breathes deeply)

17:26.797 --> 17:28.549
Total honesty.

17:29.591 --> 17:31.885
Absolute truth.

17:34.429 --> 17:36.390
Do you love me?

17:38.225 --> 17:40.769
Will you always be loyal to me?

17:43.981 --> 17:47.317
You make it so hard sometimes.

17:47.401 --> 17:50.612
It's time for you to understand

17:50.696 --> 17:54.157
your place
in the bigger picture.

17:54.241 --> 17:56.285
I must have your vow.

17:56.368 --> 17:58.495
-Yes.
-Yes?

17:58.579 --> 18:01.206
(laughs, sobs)

18:07.087 --> 18:09.256
Kai? What's wrong?

18:09.339 --> 18:12.551
I've never seen you interrupt
a pinky-power before.

18:13.427 --> 18:15.804
(Kai sobbing)

18:18.182 --> 18:20.309
I just love you so much.

18:21.393 --> 18:22.811
Our family.

18:23.645 --> 18:26.148
-You love our family?
-Yeah.

18:26.732 --> 18:28.609
The one we're going to make.

