35:55.489 --> 35:56.990
Valerie was right!

35:57.074 --> 35:58.867
You're like every man.

35:58.951 --> 36:00.786
-You're a turd.
-Be careful with that.

36:00.869 --> 36:02.371
Say it!

36:02.454 --> 36:04.248
-"I'm a turd."
-No.

36:04.331 --> 36:07.501
"I'm a lowly, abject turd!"

36:07.584 --> 36:09.294
Fuck you!

36:10.128 --> 36:12.714
When Hillary lost, I did, too.

36:13.382 --> 36:15.133
I should have fought back.

36:15.217 --> 36:17.219
I should have gotten angry.

36:17.302 --> 36:19.596
I joined this thing
and it's too late for me.

36:19.680 --> 36:22.307
And it's too late for you, too, turd.

36:22.641 --> 36:23.976
(screaming)

36:30.065 --> 36:32.067
MEN (chanting): Divine ruler.
Divine ruler. Divine ruler.

36:32.150 --> 36:34.736
KAI: Bring the betrayers to me.

36:34.820 --> 36:37.656
MEN (continuing):
Divine ruler. Divine ruler.

36:37.739 --> 36:41.076
Divine ruler.
Divine ruler.

36:41.159 --> 36:43.287
Divine ruler.

36:43.370 --> 36:45.706
Divine ruler. Divine ruler.

36:45.789 --> 36:48.292
Divine ruler.

36:48.375 --> 36:50.919
Divine ruler. Divine ruler.

36:58.635 --> 37:00.637
(panting)

37:25.954 --> 37:27.915
Flesh and blood first.

37:29.124 --> 37:30.876
Kai, what are you doing?

37:30.959 --> 37:32.628
Untie me. Let me go.

37:34.254 --> 37:35.631
Let me go.

37:37.466 --> 37:39.760
You were supposed to protect me.

37:41.220 --> 37:42.971
You were supposed to help me.

37:43.055 --> 37:44.765
I'm trying to help you.

37:44.848 --> 37:46.433
You know you can
always trust me, Kai.

37:50.646 --> 37:54.316
I know what you've been up to.

37:56.318 --> 37:59.238
You were trying to lock me up
in the loony bin, traitor.

37:59.530 --> 38:01.031
Please, I was just concerned.
You...

38:01.114 --> 38:02.574
We can talk about this.

38:02.658 --> 38:04.660
It's not too late.

38:07.704 --> 38:10.457
Look at what you're doing.
This is not a healthy path.

38:10.541 --> 38:12.251
I've been chosen, Vince!

38:12.584 --> 38:15.254
People are counting on me
to lead!

38:15.337 --> 38:17.965
To light up this cesspool
and usher in a new beginning!

38:18.048 --> 38:19.216
VINCENT:
Kai, listen to me.

38:19.299 --> 38:22.386
All I want is
to see you succeed.

38:23.053 --> 38:26.431
No matter what happens, you are
my brother and I love you.

38:28.392 --> 38:29.935
I love you.

38:31.395 --> 38:33.981
Do you remember when you taught
me about pinky-power?

38:35.607 --> 38:39.486
Yes. It was our
own private world.

38:39.570 --> 38:41.572
And when we were
locked together...

38:42.656 --> 38:44.783
didn't matter what we did.

38:45.200 --> 38:48.120
All would be forgiven
if you just told the truth.

38:48.203 --> 38:50.330
That's right.

38:57.713 --> 39:00.340
(Kai exhales)

39:17.858 --> 39:20.903
We never lied to each other.

39:20.986 --> 39:23.071
Never.

39:26.283 --> 39:28.160
That's what made it so special.

39:28.452 --> 39:29.786
Yeah.

39:29.870 --> 39:32.122
(Vincent screams)

39:37.127 --> 39:38.504
Winter?

39:38.587 --> 39:39.713
Vincent.

39:42.174 --> 39:43.926
Aah!

39:44.009 --> 39:45.010
(gasps)

39:48.472 --> 39:49.473
(gurgles)

39:51.433 --> 39:53.227
(coughing)

39:57.564 --> 39:59.608
Get him out of my sight.

40:08.784 --> 40:11.036
What the fuck is going on?

40:11.119 --> 40:12.246
KAI: Beverly Hope.

40:12.329 --> 40:15.332
I had such plans for you...

40:16.792 --> 40:18.627
and you pissed it all away.

40:20.504 --> 40:21.839
Why?

40:21.922 --> 40:23.882
What are you talking about?
What did I do?

40:23.966 --> 40:25.509
You know what you did.

40:25.592 --> 40:28.512
Samuels deserved a lot better
than a cheap bullet to the head.

40:29.763 --> 40:31.181
Winter told me everything.

40:33.767 --> 40:35.352
SAMUELS:
<i>You've been working hard.</i>

40:35.435 --> 40:37.312
I'm sure one apple
wouldn't hurt.

40:37.396 --> 40:38.730
No. This is my punishment.

40:38.814 --> 40:40.440
I intend to honor it.

40:41.441 --> 40:42.693
SAMUELS:
No!

40:45.821 --> 40:47.781
Tell your brother he's next.

40:50.993 --> 40:52.494
Pack of lies.

40:52.953 --> 40:54.496
Bitch is full of shit.

40:58.208 --> 41:00.210
I chose you, Beverly!

41:01.128 --> 41:03.922
I trusted you!
I made you my equal!

41:04.006 --> 41:05.507
Why did you betray me?!

41:05.591 --> 41:08.177
You betrayed me!

41:09.344 --> 41:11.847
One day you promise me
equal partnership,

41:11.930 --> 41:15.934
the next you have me in a gulag
baking fucking cookies!

41:16.101 --> 41:19.104
Your promises mean shit!

41:21.190 --> 41:22.900
You're a fake.

41:22.983 --> 41:24.943
You don't stand
for a goddamn thing.

41:25.027 --> 41:26.486
I'm standing up
for millions of people

41:26.570 --> 41:28.197
who are finally being heard!

41:28.363 --> 41:31.283
Everything I do is in service
to the greater purpose!

41:31.366 --> 41:34.828
It's bigger than anything in our lives
and you are fucking it up!

41:34.912 --> 41:36.830
Nothing is bigger than your ego.

41:36.914 --> 41:38.624
You don't know
what the fuck you're doing

41:38.707 --> 41:40.375
from one minute to the next.

41:40.459 --> 41:42.294
You're incompetent, Kai.

41:42.377 --> 41:44.671
Just another attention whore.

41:44.755 --> 41:47.299
And if you're insecure enough
to believe Winter, well, then,

41:47.382 --> 41:49.176
just kill me now.

41:49.259 --> 41:50.511
Put me out of my misery.

41:50.594 --> 41:52.971
Because the biggest mistake
I ever made

41:53.055 --> 41:55.807
was believing in you. Turd.

41:56.767 --> 41:58.936
You were my favorite.

42:01.271 --> 42:03.106
But death is too good for you.

42:03.649 --> 42:05.400
I want you to suffer.

42:05.484 --> 42:07.402
Take her to the isolation chamber.

42:07.486 --> 42:10.531
Rot in hell, you son of a bitch.

42:19.498 --> 42:20.916
Loyalty...

42:23.085 --> 42:24.795
must be absolute.

42:25.295 --> 42:27.631
Without it, we have nothing.

42:29.550 --> 42:32.511
Now we can move forward.

42:52.698 --> 42:56.243
<i>Let's all welcome</i>
<i>our newest member.</i>
